article.headline: Stephenson-Moore scores 20 points as Stony Brook knocks off Norfolk State 84-78
article.description: — Tyler Stephenson-Moore's 20 points helped Stony Brook defeat Norfolk State 84-78 on Wednesday night.
article.linkText: Stephenson-Moore scores 20 points as Stony Brook knocks off Norfolk State 84-78
article.story: STONY BROOK, N.Y. -- — Tyler Stephenson-Moore's 20 points helped Stony Brook defeat Norfolk State 84-78 on Wednesday night. Stephenson-Moore was 6-of-10 shooting, including 5 for 8 from 3-point range, and went 3 for 4 from the line for the Seawolves (5-5). Chris Maidoh added 19 points while going 6 of 7 and 7 of 9 from the free-throw line, and he also had 12 rebounds. Keenan Fitzmorris was 3-of-5 shooting and 10 of 10 from the free-throw line to finish with 16 points. Jamarii Thomas led the Spartans (7-4) with 28 points. Norfolk State also got 13 points from Allen Betrand. Christian Ings also recorded 11 points and five assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
